_sText:
This map is based on the layout of doom2's final map GROSSE (i think it's a bonus level). i added the gameplay details for source and voila a new map is finished. many crates are breakable and there are two teleporters. Through the first one you get into a room only safed by glass (so you can be killed in there) where you can find an AWP. The second one leads the the top of itself where a M249 is.
v1.1: -added nav.-file by chizbone Credits: -offroad -chizbone (navfile)
Installation: copy the file to maps in cstrike example: x:\program files\steam\steamapps\yourusername\counterstrike source\cstrike\maps
